"The current algorithm compares the recent window with a best-observed cooling reference model. It needs at least %d raw samples in the reference model and recent window before it can compare cooling capacity reliably. You can calibrate the reference in Settings after cleaning dust or confirming the machine is healthy. Keep the app running in the background for long-term analysis; sampling is lightweight and designed for low power use. Current readiness: reference %.0f%%, recent coverage %.0f%%." = "当前算法会比较近期窗口与已观察到的最佳散热参考模型；参考模型和近期窗口各至少需要 %d 条原始样本，才能可靠判断散热能力。你可以在清灰后或确认机器健康时，到设置里校准参考。建议保持 App 在后台长期运行以获得更准确的分析；采样很轻量，按低功耗长期运行设计，可以放心使用。当前状态：参考 %.0f%%，近期覆盖 %.0f%%。";
